        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Fig.2: \"Endophilin 2, 3 and Arc Localize to Post-synaptic Sites with GluR1 in Hippocampal Neurons\"\n- \" Consistent with previous reports (Gad et al., 2000; Ringstad et al., 1999), endophilin 1 immunogold EM shows prominent localization to presynaptic vesicles (Figure 2A).\". Experimental description: - Species of neurons not stated in the paper, but traced back to PMID:861729: \"Rat hippocampal neurons in dispersed cell culture\"" ;
